title: Handle screenSize config change
message:
Handle screenSize config change

When I upped the targetSdkVersion, rotating the screen while processing
would leak the activity.  I learned that you need to include screenSize
as a configChange you handle in addition to orientation on API 13+
(3.2+).  Probably because the navigation buttons could be software
buttons and they move on rotate so the dimensions change.

title: Moved contactMap into shared code
message:
Moved contactMap into shared code

The contact map is in ExtendedApplication now and all the Activities
that use it go through that.  As a result, the map is only created for
the first activity that uses it and persists for the others (until the
Application is destroyed).  So the app is faster and the code is
cleaner/less duplication.

private instead of making a dozen accessors.
